{"tid":2439193,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"CGTN 被英國罰$241萬 指播被迫認罪片 報香港示威不中立 桂民海鄭文傑投訴亦成立","createTime":"2021-03-09T05:21:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-09T07:24:12.000Z","uid":115608,"like":28,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"91b0c3a60744fea2a46df46d2bc89093dddc4146","tid":2439193,"uid":115608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-09T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"英國通訊管理局（Ofcom）周一向中國中央電視台旗下「中國環球電視網」（CGTN）罰款共225,000英鎊（2,415,555港元），並裁定香港異見人士提出的兩宗投訴成立。<br />\n<br />\nOfcom因應英國私家偵探韓飛龍（Peter Humphrey）的投訴，向CGTN罰100,000鎊（1,073,580港元）。韓飛龍指CGTN在2013年播出他在中國被迫認罪的片段。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210309/K24RGPD425EWFNTS75Y5IW27UM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0uS1ZWHPTFMYzHtAItsjD5D7NS3so2RVt90Dpe7Ye0vWgGxnome9iZga8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FK24RGPD425EWFNTS75Y5IW27UM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0uS1ZWHPTFMYzHtAItsjD5D7NS3so2RVt90Dpe7Ye0vWgGxnome9iZga8&d=eGp%2FCvHI00KNC8mlo1MhyxckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=17f56f8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210309%2FK24RGPD425EWFNTS75Y5IW27UM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0uS1ZWHPTFMYzHtAItsjD5D7NS3so2RVt90Dpe7Ye0vWgGxnome9iZga8&h=2816ed7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210309/K24RGPD425EWFNTS75Y5IW27UM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0uS1ZWHPTFMYzHtAItsjD5D7NS3so2RVt90Dpe7Ye0vWgGxnome9iZga8</a>"},{"pid":"c17b22d6b6cd6bbf56a7e2827d3e06607b56255b","tid":2439193,"uid":115608,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"cited